column1:
Akane-chan, could you please pass the
potatoes?

Ahahaha, no need to be so formal with us!
We can keep it real.

Akane, would you mind helping me cut the
carrots?

*giggle* Well, they seem to be getting along
in there.

I guess she's warmin' up to us, huh? I seriously
didn't think that could happen when we first
met her.
It's thanks to all your efforts.
I can no longer sit idly by. I want to help too.

I've got it. I'll find an award-winning recipe
and...

Chill your circuits, Sophia! The curry always
tastes good when you make it together with
someone.

I can't believe you've all raided my house like
this... You guys have some serious nerve.

Although, I can't remember the last time this
place felt so alive.

You don't gotta answer if you don't wanna,
but... what happened with Akane's mom?

She said something about the killer too, right?
They ever get caught?

No case was ever pursued. Any suspect is way
outta my reach.

Hey, [1B]S1, would you help put the
finishing touches on this?

C'mon, off to work! It'd better be worth the
hassle.

Mmmm! So good! These vegetables in Kyoto
make curry so amazing!

Hmmm!? This IS delicious! I'll have to report
this back to Sojiro!
Yeah, I knew he'd lose it.

Curry that moves diners to tears? I wish I could
try it.
I want some too, but it's still too hot...

Don't worry, Morgana. We'll be sure to leave
some for you too.

Myeheh! The brains of the operation thinks of
everything!
I'm quite jealous of you, Meowgana.

We'd better keep our mouths shut here,
Sophia.

Anyway, how's our curry, Akane-chan?
Do you like it?

The Kamo eggplant gives
this curry an amazing flavor...

Ooh, did you just come up with a new dish!?
I can't wait to try it out!

Oh man, I could eat this all day! Time for
another round!

Not today, Futaba! I'm taking another helping
first!

All right, break it up. There's still more than
enough to go around.

It really is good... Do you think I could make it
by myself?
If you put in the practice.

I agree. You're very quick to learn; you'll be a
curry master in no time.

Mmhm! Mastering this isn't easy—you'll have to
learn how to "curry" your weight in the kitchen!

Oh, I've got an idea! Wanna take a bath later,
Akane-chan?

That's the best way for us girls to get to know
each other better! I can teach you all the super-
model secrets to glowing skin!
I'd like to learn those too! Mind if I joined you?

C'mon, how big do you think the bathroom is
here?

Akane and a few of the ladies
went off to share a bath together...
